text:
2 veg 1 meat for $4.6

Portion was small and not worth it

Looks like pricing in this coffee shop was expensive.

Not recommended, better go to the nearby hawker centre.
Atrocious mixed vegetable rice price where rice with steamed egg, stir-fried shredded potatoes (the Chinese kind like what Mala stall sells) and brinjals add up to $3.80.
